source.name: FDIC Institution Directory (ID) -- Insured Insitution Download File
source.description: The FDIC's Institution Directory (ID) download file provides a list of all FDIC-insured institutions. The file includes demographic information related to the institution such as locational detail (name, city state, etc) and operating status (active, inactive, bank class, etc). The download file also contains key financial information reported by the FDIC-insured institution.
